<title>USA: AES Corp board sets 2-for-1 stock split.</title>
<headline>AES Corp board sets 2-for-1 stock split.</headline>
<dateline>ARLINGTON, Va. 1997-07-15</dateline>
<text>
<p>Power company AES Corp said on Tuesday that it had approved a two-for-one stock split for shareholders payable August 28.</p>
<p>The company added that each shareholder will receive as a dividend one additional share of AES common stock for each share held on July 28.</p>
